---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blog" description="Expert real estate insights and market analysis for the Sunshine Coast">
  <section class="blog-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Market Insights & Blog</h1>
      <p>Expert analysis and advice from Jack McGhee</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="blog-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="blog-grid">
        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="blog-content-inner">
            <span class="blog-date">January 2026</span>
            <h2><a href="/blog/sunshine-coast-2026-data-driven-growth">The Sunshine Coast 2026: Data-Driven Growth for Property Investors</a></h2>
            <p>
              Current data from the Australian Bureau of Statistics and Sunshine Coast Council confirms 
              the region is outperforming national growth averages. Discover the official numbers driving 
              the market in 2026.
            </p>
            <a href="/blog/sunshine-coast-2026-data-driven-growth" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="blog-content-inner">
            <span class="blog-date">December 2025</span>
            <h2><a href="/blog/sunshine-coast-market-outlook-2026">The Sunshine Coast Property Market: 2026 Outlook</a></h2>
            <p>
              As we enter 2026, the Sunshine Coast continues to be one of Australia's most dynamic 
              property markets. Discover the key trends shaping the region and what they mean for 
              buyers and sellers in the year ahead.
            </p>
            <a href="/blog/sunshine-coast-market-outlook-2026" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="blog-content-inner">
            <span class="blog-date">November 2025</span>
            <h2><a href="/blog/first-time-buyer-tips">5 Essential Tips for First-Time Home Buyers</a></h2>
            <p>
              Navigating your first property purchase can be overwhelming, but it doesn't have to be. 
              Here's my expert advice to make your first home buying experience smooth and successful.
            </p>
            <a href="/blog/first-time-buyer-tips" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="blog-content-inner">
            <span class="blog-date">October 2025</span>
            <h2><a href="/blog/selling-property-sunshine-coast">Selling Your Property on the Sunshine Coast: A Strategic Guide</a></h2>
            <p>
              Learn the proven strategies that maximize property value in the Sunshine Coast market, 
              from presentation and marketing to negotiation and closing.
            </p>
            <a href="/blog/selling-property-sunshine-coast" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* Page-specific styles for blog page */
    .blog-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-deep) 0%, var(--ocean-blue) 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: -1px;
    }

    .blog-hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    }

    .blog-hero p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--sand-warm);
    }

    .blog-content {
      padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
    }

    .blog-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .blog-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .blog-image-placeholder {
      height: 250px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-light) 0%, var(--sand-warm) 100%);
    }

    .blog-content-inner {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .blog-date {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    }

    .blog-card h2 {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    }

    .blog-card h2 a {
      color: var(--ocean-deep);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      transition: color var(--transition-base);
    }

    .blog-card h2 a:hover {
      color: var(--ocean-blue);
    }

    .blog-card p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
      flex: 1;
    }

    .read-more {
      color: var(--ocean-blue);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color var(--transition-base);
    }

    .read-more:hover {
      color: var(--gold-accent);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .blog-hero h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .blog-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
